Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.16,0:02:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.83,0:02:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.56,0:02:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.16,0:02:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这首歌是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.37,0:02:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三话 夕饷（晚餐）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.71,0:02:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你 薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.71,0:02:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我洗得很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.42,0:02:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.65,0:02:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.08,0:02:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.75,0:02:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没…没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.19,0:02:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天一整天发生很多事 累了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.89,0:02:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被子铺好了 今晚就先休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.90,0:02:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.57,0:02:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰的被子呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.80,0:02:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只有一套被子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.10,0:02:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在旁边睡就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.61,0:02:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这怎么行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.14,0:03:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对薰太过意不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.61,0:03:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系 没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.51,0:03:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.18,0:03:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要薰不介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.55,0:03:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起睡也没…没关系…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.19,0:03:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总…总之…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.19,0:03:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要介意我 快睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.77,0:03:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰的被子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.37,0:03:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之 明天要回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.48,0:03:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.11,0:03:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能留在薰身边吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.58,0:03:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是 离开家太九
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,家人也会担心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.59,0:03:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.63,0:03:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且…这件事太突然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.60,0:03:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是有婚约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.50,0:03:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…也只知道小时候的小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.37,0:04:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵对我也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.57,0:04:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么…那么请现在开始了解葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.51,0:04:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并且…也告诉我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.98,0:04:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告诉我薰的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.42,0:04:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好…好了…快睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睡得真香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.27,0:04:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是太累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.47,0:04:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是小葵的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.01,0:04:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.94,0:04:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,写的时候把2丁目5号写成5丁目2号了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.21,0:04:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都破破烂烂的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.58,0:04:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵一定很珍惜地收藏着的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.12,0:04:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了来见我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.86,0:04:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并且…也告诉我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.13,0:05:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告诉我薰的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.00,0:05:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.05,0:05:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.65,0:05:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能因为一时的冲动而越轨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.32,0:05:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,头脑得冷静一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.95,0:05:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好烫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.12,0:05:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.70,0:05:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使说是婚约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.06,0:05:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我连女朋友都还没交过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.50,0:05:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然有了妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.27,0:05:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 小葵也不是个坏女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 接受小葵的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.52,0:05:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就得要回花菱家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.19,0:06:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱 花菱吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.76,0:06:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.56,0:06:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.03,0:06:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.50,0:06:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵 怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.33,0:06:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为门开着…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.90,0:06:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然担心薰是不是走掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.24,0:06:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.55,0:06:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.25,0:06:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不会走掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.95,0:06:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说的也是 我真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.39,0:06:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.83,0:06:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被吟唱传承下来的优美词句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.07,0:06:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…
