Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.44,0:07:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爷爷 妈妈要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.31,0:07:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快留住妈妈 留住妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.78,0:07:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快 爷爷 妈妈要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.19,0:07:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要 我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.03,0:07:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要哭哭啼啼到什么时候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.33,0:07:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘掉那种女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.90,0:07:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是花菱家的继承者 懂吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.74,0:08:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不懂 我不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.98,0:08:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种事 我一点也不懂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.15,0:08:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶 又是那个梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.42,0:08:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.20,0:08:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么小葵会和我在一个被窝里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.37,0:08:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之 不快分开的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好…舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.04,0:08:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呼吸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.15,0:08:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太可爱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.16,0:08:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然穿着和服看不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.26,0:08:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵的胸部真丰满啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不对…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.97,0:08:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想办法分开的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.00,0:09:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,万一被小葵误解了的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.24,0:09:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.04,0:09:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要逃 你这个混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.58,0:09:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇 相当漂亮的一击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.78,0:09:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挑战者危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.22,0:09:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等…等等…小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.70,0:09:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千钧一发啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.40,0:09:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次是腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.44,0:09:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要 这个地方 放过我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.58,0:09:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,投降了 冠军投降了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.45,0:09:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早…早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.73,0:09:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰…薰 怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.87,0:10:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但为什么小葵在我的被子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.14,0:10:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…那是因为昨晚薰看起来很冷的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.44,0:10:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我靠在薰的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.18,0:10:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我睡着时有抱着什么东西的习惯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.45,0:10:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱了…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.12,0:10:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 用尽全力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.65,0:10:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对…对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.99,0:10:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 薰也很冷的样子抱住我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.89,0:10:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 我们算彼此扯平了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.63,0:10:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是…不是什么彼此扯平的问题…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.80,0:10:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请用餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看样子真好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.54,0:11:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 擅自用了冰箱里的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.75,0:11:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧 不要在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.02,0:11:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该没有什么材料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.92,0:11:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能做出这样的菜 真是厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.92,0:11:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.59,0:11:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.23,0:11:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.49,0:11:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.66,0:11:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等会儿我送你到车站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.23,0:11:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我反正也要去大学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.67,0:11:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这…刚才跟家里联络过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.24,0:11:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以在这里多留些时间…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.84,0:11:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会给你添麻烦吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.84,0:11:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那倒不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.35,0:11:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么请让我送薰到车站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.82,0:11:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰总是这个时间去大学吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.06,0:11:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 今天的课是第二节开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.06,0:11:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才可以这么悠哉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.73,0:11:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.98,0:12:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…那个…薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.98,0:12:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 没…没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.19,0:12:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请不要在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.29,0:12:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.03,0:12:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰 什么时候会回来？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.40,0:12:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想应该不会很晚 怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.07,0:12:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很想替薰做晚餐 可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.47,0:12:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚餐？我的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.14,0:12:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.68,0:12:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全没有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.15,0:12:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种事倒是应该我来拜托你才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.42,0:12:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.32,0:12:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么 晚饭以前我一定会回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.12,0:12:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请慢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.26,0:12:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.86,0:13:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 要加油了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.74,0:13:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我走了…吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.58,0:13:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次说这句话是什么时候的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.19,0:13:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.80,0:13:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要些什么？太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.37,0:13:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌 什么太太 我还没…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.30,0:13:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.97,0:13:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请给我参鱼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.31,0:13:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.54,0:13:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样都齐全了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.75,0:13:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 做晚饭前 先要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.95,0:13:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.53,0:14:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.93,0:14:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,堆积了这样多衣服没洗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.97,0:14:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（Aio三月号 获取他的心的方法）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.75,0:14:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵 会做怎样的晚饭呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.54,0:14:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是梦…吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 花菱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.61,0:14:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天的聚餐不要迟到哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.81,0:14:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聚餐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.05,0:14:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.05,0:14:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次不是说过了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.28,0:14:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.55,0:14:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你当然会来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.12,0:15:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.49,0:15:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 今天突然有急事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.16,0:15:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么 花菱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.16,0:15:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是说了摄影社的人全部出席的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.79,0:15:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.16,0:15:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次我一定会到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.60,0:15:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.81,0:15:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟薰在一起的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.54,0:15:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,时间就会过得那么快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.21,0:15:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然稍微早了点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.02,0:15:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.66,0:15:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.49,0:15:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎回来 薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.59,0:15:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.10,0:15:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵 怎么会在这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.33,0:15:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为晚餐准备好了所以来这里等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.33,0:15:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 我应该没说过几点会回来才对…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.44,0:15:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道 你一直在这等？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.61,0:15:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.21,0:16:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等了多久？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.81,0:16:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.18,0:16:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一小时左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.55,0:16:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等了一小时！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.18,0:16:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在房间里等就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.62,0:16:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.05,0:16:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.19,0:16:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想早一点和薰在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.22,0:16:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.59,0:16:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想到再一下子就能在这里见到薰 时间一下就过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.06,0:16:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.51,0:16:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.51,0:16:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.28,0:16:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有个请求…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.88,0:16:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请求？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.25,0:16:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以跟你牵手吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.99,0:16:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.66,0:16:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰的手真的好大…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.93,0:16:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算大吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.50,0:17:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 但是我知道的薰的手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.07,0:17:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是小时候的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.08,0:17:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然会变大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.51,0:17:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说的话 小葵也变了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.25,0:17:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我变了很多？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.95,0:17:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.69,0:17:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.79,0:17:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变得很漂亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.39,0:17:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌 薰真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.30,0:17:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请用餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.74,0:17:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇 好好吃的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.31,0:17:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.74,0:17:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵 这个是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.18,0:17:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,筑前煮（注：地方菜名）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.18,0:17:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.58,0:17:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合你口味吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.95,0:17:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吃 非常好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.89,0:17:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.46,0:17:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请多吃些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.56,0:17:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.30,0:18:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能吃到这么好吃的菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.30,0:18:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是离开花菱家后的第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.33,0:18:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.94,0:18:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 平常一直吃杯面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.14,0:18:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有钱的时候就吃面包的硬边过日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.01,0:18:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面包的硬边？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.31,0:18:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道只吃这些？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.31,0:18:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 男人的单身生活就是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.95,0:18:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不吃营养的东西 薰会死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.56,0:18:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太夸张了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.39,0:18:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 请再多吃点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.90,0:18:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也有准备薰喜欢的烤鱼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.57,0:18:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.64,0:18:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜欢的烤鱼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.81,0:18:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么小葵知道我喜欢的菜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.08,0:18:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仔细一看 全都是我喜欢的菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.48,0:18:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.65,0:18:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵 为什么你会知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜欢的菜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.59,0:19:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为那时的我一直注意着薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.06,0:19:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还知道很多其他薰的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.63,0:19:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比如喜欢烤鱼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.57,0:19:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喜欢的颜色是蓝色啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.80,0:19:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喜欢短头发啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.57,0:19:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有喜欢什么歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.81,0:19:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歌？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.91,0:19:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.58,0:19:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还在奇怪为什么小葵知道妈妈唱的歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.38,0:19:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.09,0:19:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.22,0:19:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我教她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.79,0:19:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还记得啊 那首歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.69,0:19:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰教的歌怎么能够忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.13,0:19:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在也常常会唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.47,0:19:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要一唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.97,0:19:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就感觉到薰在身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.14,0:19:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论怎样的痛苦都能熬过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.71,0:19:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛苦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.44,0:19:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我为了能成为薰的妻子而努力着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.88,0:19:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为像这样待在薰的身边是我的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.98,0:20:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想为薰打扫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.82,0:20:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想为薰洗衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.53,0:20:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想亲手为薰做饭吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.50,0:20:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要是薰所希望的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.50,0:20:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什么都想要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.50,0:20:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.14,0:20:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 一个人不停地说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.54,0:20:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁没冷掉赶快吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.88,0:20:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.61,0:20:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之前我都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.95,0:20:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵对我的感情竟然到这个程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.72,0:20:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且还考虑得那么周到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.19,0:20:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚饭后洗澡水也准备好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.56,0:20:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是体贴入微
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.93,0:20:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样的话 然后就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.20,0:20:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.83,0:20:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来替你擦背
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.40,0:20:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是连这种事都发生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.84,0:20:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的就会有点动心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.71,0:21:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是小葵 这也不可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.88,0:21:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.51,0:21:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.88,0:21:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来替你擦背 可以进来吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.56,0:21:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶…？
